Everybody is at certain times.

1180
01:18:45,433 --> 01:18:48,433
You're doing something
I didn't think you could.

1181
01:18:48,477 --> 01:18:52,225
You're passing up a real tomato
because you don't want to hurt a guy.

1182
01:18:52,272 --> 01:18:55,439
If I did that,
there wouldn't be a dry eye.

1183
01:18:55,484 --> 01:18:57,523
But I'm heartbroken over it.

1184
01:18:57,569 --> 01:19:00,060
All the more reason to feel proud of it.

1185
01:19:00,113 --> 01:19:02,189
- You think so?
- Sure.

1186
01:19:02,240 --> 01:19:06,985
Listen, kid, there's other things
in life besides dames.

1187
01:19:07,036 --> 01:19:10,951
One of them is to know
you did the right thing for a pal.

1188
01:19:10,999 --> 01:19:13,074
Think it over.

1189
01:19:43,029 --> 01:19:46,861
- What gate is the flight to Cleveland?
- Gate 15.

1190
01:19:54,623 --> 01:19:57,577
- Where's the plane to Cleveland?
- Gate 15.

1191
01:20:17,479 --> 01:20:19,804
- Wait.
- What are you doing here?

1192
01:20:19,856 --> 01:20:23,438
- I've something important to tell you.
- So do l.

1193
01:20:23,484 --> 01:20:27,102
Do you realise what a wonderful thing
has happened?

1194
01:20:27,154 --> 01:20:31,448
The most beautiful thing has
happened right under our noses.

1195
01:20:31,492 --> 01:20:35,821
We've had a wonderful experience.
Doesn't that surprise you?

1196
01:20:35,871 --> 01:20:39,489
You didn't have to leave books
lying around,

1197
01:20:39,541 --> 01:20:42,246
you didn't have to have on
the proper music.

1198
01:20:42,294 --> 01:20:46,872
I even saw you in your underwear
with the days of the week on them.

1199
01:20:47,591 --> 01:20:50,591
- We have to call it quits.
- Yes, I know.

1200
01:20:50,635 --> 01:20:54,134
- Pardon me?
- Suddenly things became very clear.

1201
01:20:54,180 --> 01:20:58,842
And when I asked myself if I really
wanted to break off my marriage,

1202
01:20:58,893 --> 01:21:02,476
the answer was no. I love Dick.

1203
01:21:03,522 --> 01:21:07,306
Although someone
as wonderful as you is very tempting,

1204
01:21:07,359 --> 01:21:10,526
- I can't imagine life without him.
- You can't?

1205
01:21:10,571 --> 01:21:16,444
He needs me. In some
unexplainable way, I need him.

1206
01:21:16,494 --> 01:21:18,570
I know he needs you.

1207
01:21:18,621 --> 01:21:22,950
This is the first time I've been affected
by anyone besides Dick.

1208
01:21:23,000 --> 01:21:25,325
I'm already in love with you.

1209
01:21:25,378 --> 01:21:29,589
Unless we stop now,
I won't be able to go back to him.

1210
01:21:29,632 --> 01:21:32,668
I don't regret a moment
of what's happened

1211
01:21:32,718 --> 01:21:37,214
because it's reaffirmed
my feelings for Dick.

1212
01:21:40,434 --> 01:21:42,510
Linda, I understand, really.

1213
01:21:42,561 --> 01:21:46,261
Sure? You're not just saying that
to make things easy?

1214
01:21:46,314 --> 01:21:48,521
I'm saying it because it's true.

1215
01:21:48,566 --> 01:21:52,481
We both know you belong to Dick.
You're part of his work.

1216
01:21:52,529 --> 01:21:55,778
If that plane leaves and you don't,
you'll regret it.

1217
01:21:55,823 --> 01:22:00,615
Maybe not today or tomorrow
but soon and for the rest of your life.

1218
01:22:00,661 --> 01:22:02,535
That's beautiful.

1219
01:22:02,580 --> 01:22:04,786
It's from Casablanca.

1220
01:22:04,832 --> 01:22:07,405
I waited my whole life to say it.

1221
01:22:18,053 --> 01:22:21,137
I thought I saw you here.
What's going on?

1222
01:22:21,181 --> 01:22:24,217
You should know something
before you two leave.

1223
01:22:24,267 --> 01:22:26,972
Us? You're coming with me?

1224
01:22:28,354 --> 01:22:30,976
Nobody owes me any explanations.

1225
01:22:31,024 --> 01:22:34,724
I'm going to anyway because
it may mean something later on.

1226
01:22:34,777 --> 01:22:38,110
You said you thought Linda
was having an affair.

1227
01:22:38,155 --> 01:22:41,192
But she was at my house
when you called.

1228
01:22:41,242 --> 01:22:45,820
She came over to baby-sit with me
because I was lonely. Right?

1229
01:22:47,539 --> 01:22:50,706
Over the past weeks
I've fallen in love with her.

1230
01:22:50,751 --> 01:22:55,543
I hoped she felt the same way
but all she could talk about was you.

1231
01:22:55,589 --> 01:22:58,922
- I understand, Allan.
- I hope you do.

1232
01:23:13,356 --> 01:23:15,562
We better be going.

1233
01:23:23,532 --> 01:23:25,608
I'll call you, Allan.

1234
01:23:39,964 --> 01:23:42,040
That was great.

1235
01:23:42,091 --> 01:23:45,507
You've really developed yourself
a little style.

1236
01:23:45,553 --> 01:23:48,673
I do have a certain amount of style,
don't l?

1237
01:23:49,765 --> 01:23:52,636
I guess you won't be needing me
any more.

1238
01:23:52,685 --> 01:23:57,181
There's nothing I can tell you now
that you don't already know.

1239
01:23:57,231 --> 01:24:01,857
I guess that's so. I guess the secret's
not being you, it's being me.

1240
01:24:01,902 --> 01:24:04,653
True, you're not too tall and kinda ugly

1241
01:24:04,696 --> 01:24:09,903
but I'm short enough and ugly enough
to succeed on my own.

1242
01:24:12,245 --> 01:24:14,534
Here's looking at you, kid.